{"tid":2344114,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【有片】車禍現場！張柏芝商演沒彩排，失聲毀掉招牌歌","createTime":"2020-12-28T12:36:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-30T22:33:37.000Z","uid":38539,"like":6,"dislike":163,"uniUserReply":92,"replies":[{"pid":"511e8aed95860386448006270905fe9d5dd2bb81","tid":2344114,"uid":38539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T12:36:14.000Z","msg":"裡面有片<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201228/PTXDHOEFJZHFBNUDPTTYYVVQEI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201228%2FPTXDHOEFJZHFBNUDPTTYYVVQEI%2F&d=vFDcqKLMx6N8Vlwxc9Uzx1tf78QfJQp2bpA%2BRTfa5cI%3D&h=2ffd5276\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Fentertainment%2F20201228%2FPTXDHOEFJZHFBNUDPTTYYVVQEI%2F&h=12e713e5\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/entertainment/20201228/PTXDHOEFJZHFBNUDPTTYYVVQEI/</a><br />\n<br />\n日前傳張柏芝名列第2季《乘風破浪的姐姐》演出名單，將比拚唱跳實力爭取組團出道，她前晚（26日）現身廣州商演，卻製造「車禍現場」，演唱招牌歌《星語心願》時聲音嘶啞又頻頻卡住，過程慘不忍睹。<br />\n<br />\n原來她當天喉嚨狀況不佳，一登場就向觀眾道歉說自己失聲了，接著表示：「不好意思，我們沒有彩排過，我會盡我的努力，希望你們可以多多包涵。」開始表演後，第一段卻是對嘴，還可看出她嘴型對不準，第二段她清清喉嚨才呈現現場原音，果然很沙啞，後來她一度搶拍，回頭看向工作人員，接著往後退，摀著耳朵指向前方說「在這裡聽不到」，讓人傻眼。<br />\n<br />\n雖然她身體抱恙仍堅持把歌唱完，讓她的粉絲很感動，不過她沒彩排就上場，過程頻頻出槌，若以同樣態度上《乘風破浪的姐姐》恐怕凶多吉少。"},{"pid":"a6f97410ea54ad82311c6f25f3cb76e4c1cc514c","tid":2344114,"uid":182543,"like":613,"dislike":5,"score":608,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T12:38:58.000Z","msg":"喉嚨狀況不佳都幾十年仲未好？"},{"pid":"20b98a8f907dd959844597e786591573cfdf8655","tid":2344114,"uid":212623,"like":4,"dislike":3,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T12:40:15.000Z","msg":"新片牛油果沙到<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c53c4537d0e8440e70d910a5956f555ecbee16a","tid":2344114,"uid":92299,"like":80,"dislike":17,"score":63,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T12:40:22.000Z","msg":"Sor, 比我啲精漿著咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/wail_r